data.text:
Roger Dean O'Donnell, of Spring Lake Park, passed away at home on Wednesday, February 20, 2019. He was 86 years old. Army veteran. Worked many years for Burlington Northern RR.

Roger was preceded in death by his children, Timothy, James, and Debra; sister, Nancy; brother, Neil.

He is survived by his loving wife of 61 years, Carole; children, DeAnn (Roy) Sullins and Michael (Mary) O'Donnell; 6 grandchildren; 6 great-grandchildren; sisters, Marion Brinken and Kay Krentz; other loving family and friends.
